text: Guillermo Durán and Máximo González were the defending champions, but Durán did not participate this year. González defended his title alongside Flavio Cipolla, beating Andreas Beck and Peter Gojowczyk 6–4, 6–1. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==External links== * Main Draw Distal and ITR Group Tennis Cup - Doubles 2015 Doubles
